docs.snippet: Reorganization of the State Department through abolition of the Mexican division and consolidation of its functions with those of the LatinAmerican division into a new division to be known as the division of the American Republics was announced by...
docs.lead_paragraph: Reorganization of the State Department through abolition of the Mexican division and consolidation of its functions with those of the LatinAmerican division into a new division to be known as the division of the American Republics was announced by Secretary Hull today coincident with the assignment of duties to the Under-Secretary and Counselor of the department.
